beer.beer_description: Brewed with a holy purpose, this beer packs a punch so strong that Beelzebub himself drops to the floor and quivers at the mere sight of it. Double the strength of some of the earliest Bocks and with a toasty nut-like character, this beer can sustain a monk through months of fasting-with enough hop character from contemporary hops to smother the fires of Hades. The monks of old believed that liquids cleansed the body and the soul. Amen brothers and sisters, redemption is here.
